# Keep Vercel's FastAPI auto-detection from triggering. The serverless function
# (api/report.py) imports the hypersignal engine from src/** via includeFiles and
# installs deps from requirements.txt — it never imports these FastAPI/typer
# `app` modules, and dropping them (+ pyproject.toml) removes every signal that
# made Vercel try to deploy a FastAPI backend instead of our static SPA.
pyproject.toml
src/hypersignal/serve.py
src/hypersignal/cli.py

